pro_course_detail.description:
Let's make your English better together! 

These lessons are for you if:

- you are studying English on your own and you need to practice speaking;
- you already speak English and don't want to lose your speaking skills or you just want to become more confident while speaking;
- you would like to practice speaking on a certain topic;
- you want to discuss anything else.

